                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, A</hi> 237). I produce a certificate of the con<lb></lb>viction of the prisoner Vickers by the name of John Long—(read)—<hi rend="italic">Con<lb></lb>fided Dec</hi>, 1848, <hi rend="italic">confined six months</hi>)—he is the man.</p>
